extendedInfo.description: At eNannySource.com thereâs nothing we love more than facilitating the perfect match of family and nanny. Weâve been in the nanny business since 1994 using what we learned at our own nanny agency to develop eNannySource.com.  Over the years we have helped over 450,000 members with nanny placements while continuing to offer personal services as needed.Along the way, we found that most families can screen nannies just as well as nanny agencies as long as we provide them with the right tools.  This allows them to get the care they need without paying the high prices of a local nanny agency.  In addition to a great database we also offer several toolkits and guides including our Nanny Success Kit, comprehensive background checks including driving records, and pretty much everything that you would expect when working with a professional agency.Our online process is simple, free to try, and very effective.  In addition to great online tools we recognized that there was a need for people to be able to quickly search for nannies and families on the go.  We created our mobile applications to solve that requirement.  All you have to do is provide your zip code and then search our database right from your mobile device.  Now it's even easier for families and nannies to find that perfect match.
